<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="content-adj">content <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'tent/    美 /kən'tent/  </p>
<p>[不用于名词前]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>满意的；满足的：</strong></h4>
<p>happy and satisﬁed：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Happy is he who is content.
知足者常乐。</p><footer>2013 天津</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) content with:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I am content with second place, because I know that I tried my hardest.
得第二名我就知足了，因为我知道自己已经尽最大努力了。</p><footer>译林⑥ – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Not content with a big house, a loving family, Selina still tries to build her own career.
赛琳娜不满足于有个大房子还有其乐融融的家庭，她仍然努力创建自己的事业。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-content-for-sb-to-do-sth">(be) content (for sb) to do sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>乐得（让某人）做 某事；满足于（让某人）做某事 (willing to do sth):</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is content to live quietly by herself.
她愿意独自安静地生活。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>contentment /kən'tentmənt/ n   </p></div>